The '''Umgullian Racing Commission''' monitored the sport of [[blob racing]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], they announced the findings of a tainted blob and addressed the authorities. The [[Vob Bitas|cheater]] was subsequently convicted and killed two hours later.

